Sample New York Mayoral Election Data

Source: R/data.R
nyc.Rd

Sample New York Mayoral Election Data

Usage

nyc

Format

A data frame with 4,063 rows and 8 columns:

ad

Assembly District number

ed

Election District (precinct) identifier

obs

Time-of-night vector. Threshold to simulate whether a precinct has been observed.

mamdani

Zohran Mamdani vote share

prim25_cvr_top_m

Fraction of first-round ballots ranking Mamdani first in the primary election

votes_total_21

Total votes in the 2021 mayoral general election

p_white

Fraction of voters identifying as White alone

total

Total number of ballots cast in the current election

Examples

head(nyc)
